{"tid":2358654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年8.31一周年堵路 獲撤控准守行為","createTime":"2021-01-08T09:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:00:06.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e101786862c224077e1e08adc7b358e664c66a6","tid":2358654,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"中四男生應網上號召，於「831事件」一周年到太子港鐵站聚集，其間站出車路再用交通路標堵路，被控在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為罪。案件今於九龍城裁判法院再訊，控方同意撤控，改以簽保守行為方式處理。男生獲准自簽2,000元、守行為24個月，並須繳付300元堂費。<br />\n<br />\n有警長駕駛私家車經過時，被阻10至15秒。陳隨後向旺角道離去，並向途人揮手喊：「走喇，手足。」探員跟蹤至旺角道天橋截停拘捕被告。陳警誡下承認阻擋貨車，將路標踢向馬路。"},{"pid":"ce3c50a3bcd582cdba1f7a16e3a79761f9e97991","tid":2358654,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/C7NMSB2LEZGCNI7VPJ75RE6J4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FC7NMSB2LEZGCNI7VPJ75RE6J4A%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=6faa2c80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FC7NMSB2LEZGCNI7VPJ75RE6J4A%2F&h=a49769f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/C7NMSB2LEZGCNI7VPJ75RE6J4A/</a>"},{"pid":"6beba61c0db57aab5cc7f8e42a540debd01dbee4","tid":2358654,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ce489f9387c044b8e881f60f355b0bba202128","tid":2358654,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdff610b2163f7550ce28a80c8b1a7b1f8b69826","tid":2358654,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime